				<ol>
					<li type="a">Events of Default by Company. The following events, for whatever reason they occur (and whether such occurrence shall be voluntary or involuntary or come about or be effected by operation of law or pursuant to or in compliance with any judgment, decree, or order of any court or any order, rule, or regulation of any administrative or governmental body), shall be deemed to be "Events of Default":
						<ol type="i">
